sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant A as Agent
    participant WS as WorldState
    participant MPT as MPT (LevelDB)
    participant DED as DED API

    A ->>+ WS: insert(streamKey, eventId, stateHash)

    WS ->>+ MPT: trie.insert(path, hash)
    MPT -->>- WS: newRoot (SHA-256 digest)

    Note over WS: buildFingerprint(<br/>documentRef = newRoot,<br/>documentId = parent:{prevHash}:ordinal:{N})

    Note over WS: sign(fingerprint, privateKey)<br/>SECP256K1_RFC8785_V1

    WS ->>+ DED: POST /v1/fingerprints
    DED -->>- WS: { hash, accepted: true }

    Note over WS: updateChainState(<br/>streamKey, hash, ordinal + 1)

    WS ->> MPT: persistTrie(streamKey)

    WS -->>- A: { fingerprintHash, ordinal, mptRoot }
